## Deck quality checklist (MANDATORY before `create_presentation`)

- [ ] 36–50+ total slides
- [ ] 8–9 section dividers with proper "Section Title" layout
- [ ] PESTEL: 6 individual slides (one per factor), each with **≥6** pre-implication bullets, **≥3** anchored facts, **≥4** slides with **level-2** clusters, **Product implication** ≥~22 words (two clauses)
- [ ] Interview: strip intro **≥6** bullets; **1** participants slide; **1** slide per customer with **≥7** lines (L1+L2), **≥2** quote-led bullets, theme + JTBD bullets per **v30 depth** block
- [ ] Themes: Split across 2 slides (1–3, 4–6 or similar)
- [ ] Triangulation: Cross-Source Validation Matrix table
- [ ] Recommendations: Individual slides (not compressed bullets)
- [ ] E2E Handoff: Numbered table slide (when report includes E2E handoff)
- [ ] Speaker notes on all content slides (except Title, Section Title, Bumper)
- [ ] Chart font sizes set (`category_axis_font_size_pt: 9`, `value_axis_font_size_pt: 9`)
- [ ] Product implication formatting (PESTEL slides)
- [ ] **Agenda (slide 2):** no `[{` / `'text':` artefacts; Section Title **subtitles** are plain strings with **12–22 word** `Section | substance` lines

**If any checklist item fails, revise `slides_spec_vN.json` before calling `create_presentation`.**

